import React from 'react'
import '../../App.css';
function Form() {
  return (
    <>
    <form>
          <input
              className='footer-input'
              name='email'
              type='email'
              placeholder='Your Email'
            />
            <input
              className='footer-input'
              name='email'
              type='password'
              placeholder='Password'
            />
            <Button buttonStyle='btn--outline'>Subscribe</Button>
          </form>
    </>
  )
}

export default Form
